This the supplementary material no. 2 for the article Comparative Statistical Analysis of Qualitative Parametrization Sets, published in proceedings of the conference Hybrid Systems Biology 2015.

This material features the case study of hepatocyte growth factor signalling based on the study "Disentangling the Complexity of HGF Signaling by Combining Qualitative and Quantitative Modeling" by D'Allesandro et al., Plos Computational Biology, 2015.
